            "stanza_number": 2,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 5,
                    "line_text": "Seul au fond d’une vaste plaine,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 6,
                    "line_text": "De loin il me montrait des fleurs ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 7,
                    "line_text": "Et mes pieds me portaient à peine ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 8,
                    "line_text": "Et ma voix s’écoulait en pleurs.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Seul au fond d’une vaste plaine,\nDe loin il me montrait des fleurs ;\nEt mes pieds me portaient à peine ;\nEt ma voix s’écoulait en pleurs."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 3,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 9,
                    "line_text": "Mon cœur s’épuisait à l’attendre,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 10,
                    "line_text": "Les chemins se changeaient en flots ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 11,
                    "line_text": "J’exhalais son nom sans m’entendre,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 12,
                    "line_text": "Je ne criais que des sanglots.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Mon cœur s’épuisait à l’attendre,\nLes chemins se changeaient en flots ;\nJ’exhalais son nom sans m’entendre,\nJe ne criais que des sanglots."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 4,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 13,
                    "line_text": "Il regarde, il pleure, il s’arrête.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 14,
                    "line_text": "« Tu le veux, dit-il, me voilà ! »",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 15,
                    "line_text": "Des ailes planaient sur ma tête :",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 16,
                    "line_text": "Il était ange… et s’envola.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
